{"tid":656893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港其實好似韓國世越號","createTime":"2018-05-07T15:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T15:31:55.000Z","uid":112205,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b83d630255633b5f9558b59dc0975328e76ccd","tid":656893,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"大家都睇到香港有好多問題<br />\n就好似韓國世越號，係迷霧中仲要出海<br />\n香港依艘船 已經係沉緊<br />\n文化、政治、生活方式、語言、經濟<br />\n都沉緊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地年輕一代的香港人<br />\n就好似世越號既學生 <br />\n<br />\n船長同人講無事既 留係原地 點知自己最快走<br />\n就似香港高官 講愛國 但屋企成家都係外國人<br />\n講教育局長 話香港教育勁  點知自己小朋友讀國際學校<br />\n<br />\n如果我地冇批判思維<br />\n我地同韓仔一樣服從指令<br />\n最後一齊死係架船到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b69947cbba782beb0044cc57a79b70e6b964dd","tid":656893,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"最重要係成單沉船都係政府一手策劃嘅祭天儀式<br />\n我地生不由己"},{"pid":"b65d20f4b7548e9d4c15292a683a708f63b1dd57","tid":656893,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b69947cbba782beb0044cc57a79b70e6b964dd","tid":656893,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"最重要係成單沉船都係政府一手策劃嘅祭天儀式<br />\n我地生不由己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"祭比共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}